Rulings.Base:
1. If you choose to activate this effect you must Summon at least 1 Token.
2. You don't have to choose the number of Tokens you want to Summon until the effect resolves.
3. You don't count your opponent's monsters until the effect resolves.
4. If a "Compass Token" is affected by "Limiter Removal" it will be destroyed during the End Phase even if its ATK stayed at 0.
